            <article id="post-28577" class="post-28577 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-lanzamientos-cat tag-4x4 tag-all-new-maverick tag-camioneta tag-ford tag-ford-peru tag-lanzamiento tag-pick-up">
